premise_source_doc_sentence: In 2005 he founded The Museum of the American Cocktail in New Orleans , an eclectic collection of cocktail artifacts , books , and memorabilia .

The Museum of the American Cocktail , based in New Orleans , Louisiana , is a nonprofit organization dedicated to education in mixology and preserving the rich history of the cocktail as developed in the United States .
It annually presents the American Cocktail Awards  (  the `` Olives ''  )  , together with the United States Bartenders Guild .
Dale DeGroff  (  born September 21 , 1948 , Rhode Island  )  , aka King Cocktail , is a US-American bartender and author .

He is the author two best selling cocktail books : The Essential Cocktail  (  Random House  )  , winner of the 2009 Tales of the Cocktail Spirit Awards , and The Craft of the Cocktail  (  Random House  )  , winner of the 2002 IACP Julia Child Award .
